            var seed = Math.random();

                window[seed] = null;
                img.onload = img.onerror = null;

        return function(arg, url, e){
            var s = URL + json2Query(arg) + '&' + Math.random();
            request(s);
            if(url){
                setTimeout(function(){
                    location.href = url;
                }, 300);
                e = e || window.event;
                if(e){
                    if(e.preventDefault){
                        e.preventDefault();
                    }else{
                        e.returnValue = false;

                }

            }
        };

        if(json == null || typeof json != 'object') return json;

        }
        return query.join('&');
    }
